{"tid":1614550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登幾時肯開個國際台or英文台","createTime":"2019-10-02T22:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T09:00:20.000Z","uid":224007,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b930656f72684c22d47b4312d791fd93b1f7de95","tid":1614550,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T22:48:58.000Z","msg":"除左香港本土戰線之外，外國巴打絲打好多時想幫手分享啲英文文宣都發覺完全唔集中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際戰線，例如住美國 加拿大 英國既手足有時想推外國既行動post都唔知post去邊好。有時有啲外國消息post又好快沉<br />\n<br />\n不如加個國際台或者英文台集中啲，等多啲其他國家既人or記都睇到香港既情況，吸引多啲全球關注咪仲好<br />\n<br />\n讚成既推下唔該！比連仔知道國際戰線一樣重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f88dc50c134deba1ab7bed024125e825122a3b","tid":1614550,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T22:49:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a75bf8bb3c44ad86085466627941abc6111060e3","tid":1614550,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T22:50:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83becd101534f7c3cea66f8c3b99cbafd0949a12","tid":1614550,"uid":224007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:17:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"407148e9819858f4b8746b85d687f8db8550517f","tid":1614550,"uid":62350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:39:16.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568382b5fc033d3998c23856d93bb7230950fbf5","tid":1614550,"uid":62350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:39:30.000Z","msg":"學下英文都好"},{"pid":"fbe29da2a5fd3365efbd4b4f5ecf27455f2a3a85","tid":1614550,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:40:09.000Z","msg":"please"},{"pid":"29b36187f446c36200bb66bf4387b69d8ea541ad","tid":1614550,"ui